snippet.textDisplay: Honestly, I think we've all been Nolan at some point. It's been such an adventure in this series watching Nolan learn a ton and realizing all the looks of fear and shame are all things we've felt and been through working on our cars. Hoping everything holds together, hearing all your buds heckling when stuff doesn't work out, taking that in stride... This is what car culture needs. All of these guys at Donut are some of the coolest and most supportive people to each other and more people need to see the support they give to one another and help lift car culture out of the pit it's been in for years. Cheers, Donut, car culture needs you!
